Robert Knapp (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Knapp_(actor) 0 Robert Knapp (February 24, 1924, Los Angeles, California – May 17, 2001, Glendale, California) was an American actor who appeared in film and on television between 1951 and 1976.
